bhrūlalāṭasaṃkocaṃ ca prasādahānikaraṃ tyajet. pūrvam eva asaṃcodita eva pareṇa svāgatādivādaiḥ saṃtoṣaṇaśīlo bhavet. sarvasattvānām akāraṇabāndhavaś ca.

<commentary>ity api śikṣānarthavarjanāya kāryety āha.

sahasā tvaritam eva niṣprayojanaṃ hastadaṇḍādinā kapāṭaṃ ca nākoṭayet. saṃkṣepataḥ niḥśabdābhiratir bhavet ||</commentary>

kaḥ evaṃ sati guṇaḥ syād ity āha. ete sarve niḥśabdā anuddhatāś ca viharanto vivakṣitam arthaṃ labhante.
